I've always wanted to split myself up into multiple copies so that one can nap, one can walk the dog, and one can do the dishes. Then I stopped to think what would happen if one of those copies died, and this was born.

Big thank you to everyone on the Drafts forum who helped me polish this, and those who helped with narrowing down research on that board as well.







